    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ornamentation composed of parallel convex moldings, particularly popular in the late 18th and early 19th centuries for furniture and silverwork.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
